      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"shopify-section-template--19607468179624__Shipping-arai\" class=\"shopify-section py-12\"><div class=\"shipping-policy\">\n\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n  <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold text-black mb-10'>Shipping Policy</h1>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"8\" width=\"18\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\"/><path d=\"M12 8v13\"/><path d=\"M19 12v9H5v-9\"/><path d=\"M7.5 8a2.5 2.5 0 1 1 0-5C11 3 12 8 12 8s1-5 4.5-5a2.5 2.5 0 1 1 0 5z\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Free Shipping &amp; Order Processing\n  </h3>\n  <p>Enjoy <strong>FREE Australia-wide shipping</strong> on <strong>online orders</strong> over <strong>$499 AUD</strong> (unless otherwise stated in a promotion).</p>\n  <p>Orders placed Monday to Friday are typically processed and dispatched within <strong>24–48 hours</strong>. If an unexpected delay occurs, our team will contact you with an updated estimated dispatch timeframe.</p>\n  <p>Once your order has shipped, you'll receive a confirmation email with tracking details so you can monitor your delivery.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><polyline points=\"12 7 12 12 16 14\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Delivery Timeframes\n  </h3>\n  <p>Estimated delivery times below apply once your order has been dispatched from our warehouse.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"delivery-box\">\n    <table>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><th>Region</th><th>Metro Areas</th><th>Regional Areas</th></tr>\n        <tr><td>NSW</td><td>1–2 Business Days</td><td>2–3 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>VIC</td><td>1–2 Business Days</td><td>2–3 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>QLD</td><td>1–2 Business Days</td><td>2–3 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>SA</td><td>1–2 Business Days</td><td>2–4 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>TAS</td><td>3–4 Business Days</td><td>4–5 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>WA</td><td>4–5 Business Days</td><td>6–7 Business Days</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>NT</td><td>4–5 Business Days</td><td>5–7 Business Days</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <p><strong>Please Note:</strong> Delivery estimates may vary due to courier schedules, weather conditions, peak periods, or remote-location factors.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 8 12 3 3 8v8l9 5 9-5z\"/><path d=\"M3 8l9 5 9-5\"/><path d=\"M12 13v8\"/><path d=\"M7.5 5.5l9 5\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Special Order &amp; Back-Ordered Items\n  </h3>\n  <p>Some products may be classified as special order or temporarily back-ordered from our suppliers.</p>\n  <p>Where this occurs:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Orders are generally held until all items are available for dispatch</li>\n    <li>Typical supplier restock timeframes are up to 10 business days</li>\n    <li>We will notify you if extended delays are expected</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>For warehouse, commercial site, or bulk freight deliveries, customers must ensure appropriate unloading access is available. Additional freight charges may apply where special handling is required.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"5\" width=\"18\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"10\"/><line x1=\"7\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Shipping Rates\n  </h3>\n  <p>Shipping costs are automatically calculated at checkout based on:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Delivery location</li>\n    <li>Product dimensions &amp; weight</li>\n    <li>Order size</li>\n    <li>Freight requirements</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Eligible orders may qualify for free standard shipping promotions; however, exclusions apply.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><line x1=\"5.5\" y1=\"5.5\" x2=\"18.5\" y2=\"18.5\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Free Shipping Exclusions\n  </h3>\n  <p>Free shipping promotions do not apply to:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Bulky items</li>\n    <li>Oversized products</li>\n    <li>Heavy freight items</li>\n    <li>Freight-only products</li>\n    <li>Certain regional or remote delivery locations</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Some products may require additional freight charges due to their:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Weight</li>\n    <li>Dimensions</li>\n    <li>Handling requirements</li>\n    <li>Delivery location</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>If additional freight charges apply, our team will contact you after checkout to provide a freight quote prior to dispatch.</p>\n  <p><em>eSafety Supplies reserves the right to cancel and refund orders where shipping costs are significantly higher than standard delivery rates.</em></p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\"/><rect x=\"13\" y=\"7\" width=\"8\" height=\"12\"/><rect x=\"7\" y=\"3\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Bulky &amp; Oversized Items\n  </h3>\n  <p>Certain products sold by eSafety Supplies are classified as bulky or oversized.</p>\n  <p>These items may:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Incur additional freight charges</li>\n    <li>Require specialised courier arrangements</li>\n    <li>Experience longer delivery timeframes</li>\n    <li>Be excluded from free shipping promotions</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Freight costs for bulky items may vary depending on your location, particularly for regional and remote areas.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-7.5 8-13a8 8 0 0 0-16 0c0 5.5 8 13 8 13z\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"9\" r=\"3\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Remote Area Deliveries\n  </h3>\n  <p>Additional shipping charges may apply for deliveries to remote or regional areas across Australia.</p>\n  <p>If extra freight charges are required, we will contact you before dispatch to confirm the updated shipping cost.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 9a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h8a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v9H4z\"/><path d=\"M12 5v8\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"21\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    No PO Box Deliveries\n  </h3>\n  <p>Due to size, weight, and courier restrictions, we are unable to deliver to PO Boxes. All orders must be shipped to a valid street address.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\"/><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y2=\"16.65\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Order Tracking\n  </h3>\n  <p>Tracking information will be emailed once your order has been dispatched.</p>\n  <p>Please allow up to 24 hours for tracking updates to appear within the courier's system.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"22 12 16 12 14 15 10 15 8 12 2 12\"/><path d=\"M5.45 5.11 2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Authority To Leave (ATL)\n  </h3>\n  <p>If Authority To Leave (ATL) is selected at checkout or authorised directly with the courier, parcels may be left unattended at the delivery address.</p>\n  <p>Once delivery has been completed by the courier, eSafety Supplies is not responsible for parcels that are lost, stolen, or damaged.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><line x1=\"9\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"15\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Failed Deliveries &amp; Returned Parcels\n  </h3>\n  <p>Orders may be returned to us if delivery is unsuccessful due to:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Incorrect shipping details</li>\n    <li>Failed collection attempts</li>\n    <li>Restricted site access</li>\n    <li>Inability to safely deliver the parcel</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Additional re-delivery charges may apply for returned parcels.</p>\n  <p>Please ensure all shipping information is accurate before placing your order.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"13\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"17\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Damaged or Lost Shipments\n  </h3>\n  <p>If your order arrives damaged or is lost in transit, please contact us as soon as possible at:</p>\n  <p><a href=\"mailto:support@esafetysupplies.com.au\">support@esafetysupplies.com.au</a></p>\n  <p>To assist with claims, please include photos of:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>The product</li>\n    <li>Packaging</li>\n    <li>Shipping label</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>We will work with the courier to investigate and resolve the issue where applicable.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"/><path d=\"M12 3a14 14 0 0 1 0 18M12 3a14 14 0 0 0 0 18\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    International Shipping\n  </h3>\n  <p>Currently, eSafety Supplies ships within Australia only.</p>\n\n  <h3 class=\"heading-with-icon\">\n    <span class=\"section-icon\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 16.92V20a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.18 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.18 2h3.08a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    Contact Us\n  </h3>\n  <p>If you have any questions regarding shipping, freight charges, or delivery timeframes, please contact our customer support team.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"contact-buttons\">\n    <a href=\"tel:1300291700\" class=\"contact-btn\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 16.92V20a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.18 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.18 2h3.08a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"/></svg>\n      1300 291 700\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"mailto:support@esafetysupplies.com.au\" class=\"contact-btn\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"5\" width=\"18\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/><polyline points=\"3 7 12 13 21 7\"/></svg>\n      support@esafetysupplies.com.au\n    </a>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>Thank you for choosing eSafety Supplies — we're committed to fast, reliable and secure delivery.</p>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.shipping-policy {\n  font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  max-width: 1180px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  text-align: left;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n}\n\n.shipping-policy h2 {\n  margin-top: 1.5rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  font-size: 3rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  line-height: 1.15;\n}\n\n.shipping-policy h3 {\n  margin-top: 2rem;\n  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n  font-size: 1.25rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.shipping-policy ul {\n  list-style: disc;\n  padding-left: 1.5rem;\n  margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;\n}\n\n.shipping-policy ul li {\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n.heading-with-icon {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 10px;\n}\n\n.section-icon {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  width: 28px;\n  height: 28px;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  background: #FEDC13;\n  color: #000;\n  border-radius: 6px;\n  padding: 4px;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\n.section-icon svg {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  display: block;\n}\n\n.section-icon--lg {\n  width: 36px;\n  height: 36px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  padding: 6px;\n}\n\n.delivery-box {\n  padding: 20px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  margin: 20px 0;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(3px);\n  overflow-x: auto;\n}\n\n.delivery-box table {\n  width: 100%;\n  border-collapse: collapse;\n  background-color: #fff;\n}\n\n.delivery-box th,\n.delivery-box td {\n  padding: 10px;\n  text-align: left;\n  border: 1px solid #C5C6C7;\n  background-color: #fff;\n}\n\n.delivery-box th {\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.contact-buttons {\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 10px;\n}\n\n.contact-btn {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 8px;\n  background: #FEDC13;\n  color: black;\n  padding: 10px 16px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  text-align: left;\n  transition: all 0.2s ease;\n  width: fit-content;\n  max-width: 34%;\n}\n\n.contact-btn svg {\n  width: 18px;\n  height: 18px;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.contact-btn:hover {\n  background: #000;\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.contact-btn:active {\n  background: #000;\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.shipping-policy p {\n  margin-top: 1rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .shipping-policy {\n    padding: 15px;\n    font-size: 0.95rem;\n  }\n  .shipping-policy h2 {\n    font-size: 2.25rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\n  }\n  .shipping-policy h3 {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    margin-top: 1.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n  }\n  .delivery-box {\n    padding: 15px;\n    margin: 15px 0;\n  }\n  .delivery-box th,\n  .delivery-box td {\n    padding: 8px 10px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .delivery-box table {\n    min-width: 400px;\n  }\n  .contact-buttons {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .contact-btn {\n    padding: 10px 16px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    justify-content: flex-start;\n  }\n  .section-icon {\n    width: 24px;\n    height: 24px;\n    padding: 3px;\n  }\n  .section-icon--lg {\n    width: 30px;\n    height: 30px;\n    padding: 5px;\n  }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .shipping-policy {\n    padding: 10px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .shipping-policy h2 {\n    font-size: 1.85rem;\n  }\n  .shipping-policy h3 {\n    font-size: 1rem;\n  }\n  .delivery-box {\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n  .delivery-box th,\n  .delivery-box td {\n    padding: 6px 8px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n  }\n  .delivery-box table {\n    min-width: 350px;\n  }\n  .contact-btn {\n    padding: 10px 14px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n</div>",
